(:action CleanWith
    :parameters (?a - agent ?l - location ?o - object ?ot - otype ?r - receptacle ?rt - rtype ?r2 - receptacle)
    :precondition (and
                (objectType ?o ?ot)
                (atLocation ?a ?l)
                (receptacleAtLocation ?r ?l)
                (objectAtLocation ?o ?l)
                (receptacleAtLocation ?r2 ?l)

                
                (or (not (openable ?r)) (opened ?r))  
                (or (not (openable ?r2)) (opened ?r2))                        
            
            )
    :effect (and
                (not (dirty ?o))
                
                (increase (total-cost) 1)
            )
 )

(:action RunTool
    :parameters (?a - agent ?l - location ?t - operatortool ?lOp - location ?tf - ttool ?fd - flowDest)
    :precondition (and
            (holds ?a ?tf)
            (agentAtTool ?a ?t)
            (toolAtLocation ?tf ?t ?lOp)
            (atLocation ?a ?l)
            (receptacleAtLocation ?fd ?l)
            )
    :effect (and
        (increase (tool-task-ldl:total-cost) 8)
        (operate ?t)
    )
)
